node.text:
It's time to revive our £100 MR2 and give it a glorious new life with the help of our friends @hotwheelsofficial for the 2021 Hot Wheels Legends tour 🎉

We want your input for the build, so drop some mod ideas in the comments and we might end up picking a few!

#carthrottle #hotwheels #cars #carsofinstagram #toyota #mr2 #zzw30 #jdm #carmods #carguys #cargirls

node.text:
Join us at Caffeine & Machine tomorrow evening- 10/08! 

Alex, Ethan, Jack, and Rory Reid from @autotraderuk will be at C&M tomorrow evening to finish up our trading up series. Capacity is limited, but if you manage to get in, come say hi!

node.text:
We've driven the updated Kia Stinger GT S! 🎉

It has a new active exhaust, although it's V6 still sounds pretty underwhelming.
We can forgive it for that, as the Stinger is still a riot to drive, with amusingly low traction limits even in the dry.

It feels a lot quicker than the factory figures suggest, and it's now nicer inside, with improved materials and a better infotainment system.

Sadly, it might not be around for much longer - it's thought Kia might pull the plug as early as 2022.

We'll miss it when it's gone.

#carthrottle #cars #carsofinstagram #kia #kiastinger #stingergts #kiastingergts #v6 #carguys #cargirls #petrolhead
